### User Registration
#

POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first": "first name",
  "last": "last name",
  "email": "test@mail.com",
  "password": "12345678aA",
  "locale": "ru"
}

###

GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/check-email/test@mail.com
Accept: application/json

###

POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/activate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "dvfdmf3g8blmhbv0"
}

